<@U01JK3M0Z36> <@U01JK1RUG3E>
*Single Feature MVP*
Prototype in parallel with the Upstream pilot
2/June/2021

We will develop the Single Feature _Research_ of Lefthoek’s tools. By developing this Single Feature we want to demonstrate (through 3 case scenarios or stories) the extent of Lefthoek’s capabilities, this Single Feature must be able to represent ‘the bigger picture’. Jan Hein will build the technology behind it and Elisa will do the user research. These are some of the questions or challenges we will address:
-What do people find useful in the data that we can extract?
-What is the reason they get this tool?
-What features do they need?
-What mediums can we use (articles, texts, videos, podcasts)?
-What language? What values?

text:
Title: Pilot by Lefthoek: Workshop Follow-up

Dear all,

We want to thank you again for joining Lefthoek’s Workshop last April! We gathered valuable input from all of you and now we are happy to share our insights and next steps forward.

Lefthoek in collaboration with the Upstream Festival, will release a pilot where Super Connectors like you can have a meaningful networking experience during the event. Through the "Game-Maker Challenge", we will curate a trajectory for the event’s sessions where Lefthoek steps up as the technical pillars of the experience. 

We want to invite you to an online session to introduce in detail the content of the pilot, your future role and what you gain from joining. 

We wouldn't like for any of you to miss out on this session! Please pick your preferred date and time:
<https://datumprikker.nl/pcxph8fvhf8yjiix>

We are excited to continue this process with you and we hope to see you soon!
